ActFarm Products Agencies Act
PrecisAmendments to the CANADIAN BROILER HATCHING EGG MARKETING AGENCY PROCLAMATION which will change the name of that Agency to Canadian Hatching Egg Producers, recognize the withdrawal of Alberta as a member and the dissolution of the Manitoba Broiler Hatching Egg Commission and the transfer of its powers to Manitoba Chicken Producers, and update the names of the Commodity Boards for Ontario and Quebec.
